&lt;p&gt;Aqui embaixo o Cake joga o conteúdo da view/template atual:&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;    &amp;lt;div class=&quot;container clearfix&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br /&gt;        &amp;lt;?= $this-&amp;gt;fetch('content') ?&amp;gt; &amp;lt;!-- Aqui ficará o código da view atual --&amp;gt;&lt;br /&gt;    &amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;index.ctp:&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&amp;lt;nav class=&quot;large-3 medium-4 columns&quot; id=&quot;actions-sidebar&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;
