&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Veja o restante neste artigo:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://backup/portal/cakephp-3/tutoriais/criacao-plugin-cakephp.html&quot;&gt;https://ribafs.org/portal/cakephp-3/tutoriais/criacao-plugin-cakephp.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
		<content type="html">&lt;h3&gt;11.1 - Criação de Plugin para o CakePHP 3&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;right&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A melhor maneira de melhorar o padrão de vida está em melhorar o padrão de pensamento. - U. S. Andersen&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;right&quot;&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
