&lt;p align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://book.cakephp.org/3.0/pt/orm/behaviors.html&quot;&gt;https://book.cakephp.org/3.0/pt/orm/behaviors.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://book.cakephp.org/3.0/en/orm/behaviors.html&quot;&gt;https://book.cakephp.org/3.0/en/orm/behaviors.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content>
